caller_intent: The caller (JC from Alliance Insurance) wanted to amend a policy to add a dog (shih tzu) to a client's coverage (Patricia Lena Miller, policy #5622030000).
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the caller's identity and purpose.
Agent requested policy number and dog breed details.
Agent checked the policy database using the provided policy number.
Agent confirmed the dog was already listed on the policy.
Agent informed caller no changes were needed.
summary: Alliance Insurance agent JC contacted Auto Owners Insurance to add a shih tzu to a policy. The agent confirmed the dog was already on file, resolving the request without changes. The call concluded with confirmation of existing coverage.
